 utilizes inverse equity strategies and longshort pairings the accounts they manage may invest in the following types of securities exchangelisted securities securities traded overthecounter foreign issues corporate debt securities other than commercial paper commercial paper certificates of deposit municipal securities mutual fund shares and us government securities website httpwwwmacroviewimcom executives  employees michael p lebowitz cofounder  managing director daniel jay cohen managing director  owner benjamin richard corson director of trading  operations micah patashnik director of trading  operations see our list of current and previous employees when you upgrade start my free trial ➤ see more paths to macroview investment management llc macroview investment management llc you connections via relationship science macroview investment management llc sync your contacts to see how you can connect with macroview investment management llc start my free trial ➤ see more holdings  top positions restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ investment philosophy homeabout our firminvestment philosophywhy an investor should own bondssubadvisorydocumentationcontact the advantages of working with macroview independencemacroview is independent  this means that our sole obligation is to our clients  we do not have quotas or corporate partners to support  as a feeonly investment advisor macroview charges a percentage based on assets under management  we do not receive commissions for products or securities that we r